COMMENDATIONS: Commends Chris Hansen and TruBlu Crew for helping the
Livingston Parish Sheriff's Office fight crime in Louisiana
1 A RESOLUTION
2 To commend Chris Hansen and TruBlu Crew for helping the Livingston Parish Sheriff's
3 Office fight crime in Louisiana.
4 WHEREAS, Chris Hansen is the former host of NBC Dateline's To Catch a Predator
5 series and current host of Take Down with Chris Hansen; and
6 WHEREAS, Mr. Hansen's new show recently filmed episodes at a sting house in
7 Livingston Parish; with his help, the Livingston Parish Sheriff's Office arrested thirteen men
8 in a child predator sting; and
9 WHEREAS, Livingston Parish Sheriff Jason Ard described the process as a learning
10 experience; suspects readily opened up to Mr. Hansen, which gave deputies a measure of
11 insider access that typically is not available to them; and
12 WHEREAS, the Livingston Parish Sheriff's Office, Sheriff Ard, Mr. Hansen, and the
13 TruBlu crew are most deserving of the highest recognition for their efforts to protect
14 children.
15 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
16 Legislature of Louisiana does hereby commend Chris Hansen and TruBlu Crew for helping
17 the Livingston Parish Sheriff's Office fight crime in Louisiana and does hereby extend
18 enduring appreciation for their efforts to remove predators from the state's streets.
